headline: Why Royal Caribbean (RCL) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of cruise vacation company Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) jumped 6.8% in the afternoon session after the company announced a new $2 billion share repurchase program and declared a quarterly dividend of $1.00 per share.
